Dum sacrum mystérium * cérneret Joánnes, Archángelus Míchaël tuba cécinit: Ignósce, Dómine, Deus noster, qui áperis librum, et solvis signácula ejus, allelúja.
While John was beholding * the sacred mystery, the Archangel Michael sounded with a trumpet: Forgive, O Lord our God, thou who openest the book, and loosest the seals thereof, alleluia.
